        <br />
        <p> Mr. Afolabi John is a highly experienced QSR expert. He resumed at  Tasty Food Resturant on March 3, 2014, as the Deputy Managing Director. John has a BSc. in Finance from Southern Illinois University and an MBA, with specialization in Contract & International Management. He started his career at Merrill Lynch in 1983, was assigned to the Pepsi QSR acquisition team and joined Pizza Hut where he rose to become an Area Manager. He joined Burger King and led teams to complete market turnaround for 10 years. John then worked at Popeye’s Chicken as an Operator, acquiring 2 restaurants and developing 9 additional restaurants as a Franchise Operator. John also worked for Denny's as Franchise business leader for 5 years. He joined UAC Restaurants as GM Franchise & National Operations Manager in February 2011 and was part of the turnaround of the Brand. He was the Managing Director of Special Brand, the largest Operator of Mr. Bigg's Franchise Restaurants, from June 2013 to February 2014. </p>
