        <p> Mrs. Dambo has the responsibility of ensuring compliance with Legal and Statutory regulations by the Company and its principal officers. As the Company Secretary / Legal Adviser, She also gives general support by way of legal advisory for all business units to ensure the attainment of companywide objectives. She acquired a degree in law (LL.B, Hons) from Ahmadu Bello University in 1986 and graduated from the Nigerian Law School in 1987. She acquired a Masters degree in International Law and Diplomacy from University of Lagos in 2005. She has over 20 years post-call experience cutting across Legal practice, Finance and Manufacturing sectors of the Nigerian Economy in companies like Nabisco Plc, Corporate Trust Limited and Dambo & Company (Nimibio Chambers). She was appointed Company Secretary / Legal Adviser to Tasty Plc in April, 2011 and Company Secretary / Head, Legal and Real State in 2015. </p>
